{"word":"G4913 - συνήδομαι - synḗdomai - soon-ay'-dom-ahee - Delight","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνήδομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synḗdomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-ay'-dom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Delight</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரியமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to rejoice together with"},{"paragraph":"2. once to rejoice or delight with oneself or inwardly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2237 - ἡδονή - hēdonḗ - hay-don-ay'/2237\">G2237</a>; to <i>rejoice</i> in <i>with</i> oneself, that is, <i>feel satisfaction</i> concerning: - delight.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}